        protected void encodeInExpression(java.lang.StringBuilder whereClause,
                                  AbstractSqlLikeQueryBuilder.Placeholder placeholder)
        Description copied from class: AbstractSqlLikeQueryBuilder
        Placeholders for IN queries in SQL require special treatment. This is handled at runtime by some wrapper implementations like JPAQL. But for raw queries the placeholder needs to be expanded to factor in the size of the list or array.
